collectionMetadata.name: Children's Daily Time Spent on Media Activities
collectionMetadata.description:
Data extracted from the IMDA Zero-to-Fourteen Consumer Experience Study, an annual survey conducted by IMDA that aims to understand children's (aged 0 to 14) media consumption habits.

For more information, please visit: 
https://www.imda.gov.sg/industry-development/facts-and-figures/media-consumer-experience-study
